summary: Replaces the SkyTEST's gooses with the Mihail's gray farm version.
descriptionHtml:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
SkyTEST's goose replaced with the Mihail's gray farm version.
Patch by Xtudo v0.2
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Description
===========
For me, the SkyTEST's gooses are too white and bright.
This little patch replaces them with the Mihail's gray farm version.
I did it for my game and now I'm sharing it.
If you want another replace (fowl, wild goose, bar-headed goose, etc) let me know.

ChangeLog
===========
Ver 0.1 - Release
Ver 0.2 - Updated for SkyTEST v1.65

Installation
=============
Simples:
Extract the downloaded RAR file and copy the DATA folder to your Skyrim installation folder.

Requeriments
=============
- SkyTEST - Realistic Animals and Predators.

Licensing/Legal
===============
- Thanks to Mihail and EtaYorius for their awesome work.
- Many thanks to Bethesda for making such a piece of art! I love you guys/gals! :D
